# HallKing frontend — optional config.
#
# The backend URL is normally set IN THE UI (top-bar field, saved in your browser), so you usually
# don't need this file. It exists only to document the default-resolution order:
#   1. value saved in the browser (localStorage 'hallking_backend_url')
#   2. if running the Vite dev server on :5173  -> http://localhost:8000
#   3. otherwise -> same origin (the FastAPI-served build, or your Vercel domain)
#
# On Vercel the same-origin has no backend, so paste your Colab/ngrok URL into the UI field at runtime.
